Hi Robert<br>Thanks for the infos.<br><br>In the meantime I found a workaround. <br>Instead of resized datatypes with holes I use simple vectors<br>with appropriately calculated offsets in MPI_FILE_WRITE_AT.<br>Probably not as elegant, but seems to work OK.
